{{Infobox football biography | name = Emile Linkers | image = | fullname = Emile Emanuel Anthony Linkers | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1990|9|25|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Willemstad]], [[Netherlands Antilles]] | height = {{height|m=1.80}} | position = [[Striker (association football)|Striker]] / [[Forward (association football)|Winger]] | currentclub = [[FC Lienden]] | clubnumber = 15 | youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = [[VV Baronie|Baronie]] | youthyears2 = |youthclubs2 = [[NAC Breda]] | youthyears3 = |youthclubs3 = [[RBC Roosendaal]] | years1 = 2008&ndash;2009 |clubs1 = [[NAC Breda]] | caps1 = 7 | goals1= 3 | years2 = 2009&ndash;2010 |clubs2 = [[VV Baronie|Baronie]] |caps2 = 11 |goals2 = 6 | years3 = 2010&ndash;2011 |clubs3 = [[SV ARC|ARC]] |caps3 = 15 |goals3 = 11 | years4 = 2011&ndash;2012 |clubs4 = [[PSIM Yogyakarta]] |caps4 = 16 |goals4 = 15 | years5 = 2012&ndash;2013 |clubs5 = [[PSIS Semarang]] |caps5 = 9 |goals5 = 5 | years6 = 2013&ndash;2014 |clubs6 = [[Madura United]] |caps6 = 11 |goals6 = 8 | years7 = 2014&ndash;2015 |clubs7 = [[PSGC Galuh Ciamis]] | caps7= 15 |goals7 = 13 | years8 = 2017 |clubs8 = [[Pusamania Borneo F.C.]] | caps8= 0 |goals8 = 0 | years9 = 2018 |clubs9 = [[VV Baronie|Baronie]] | caps9= 6 |goals9 = 5 | years10 = 2018– |clubs10 = [[FC Lienden]] | caps10= 1 |goals10 = 0 <!-- | totalcaps = 90 | totalgoals = 66 --> | nationalyears1 = 2014 – | nationalteam1 = [[Aruba national football team|Aruba]] | nationalcaps1 = 2 | nationalgoals1 = 1 | pcupdate = | ntupdate = 8 October 2018 }}
'''Emile Emanuel Anthony Linkers''' (born 25 September 1990) is a [[Dutch people|Dutch]] professional [[Association football|football]] player. Born in [[Willemstad]], [[Netherlands Antilles]], who plays for [[FC Lienden]].
Linkers is of [[Aruba]]n descent, from his mother's side. In 2014, he started playing for the [[Aruba national football team|national team of Aruba]]. Linkers made his debut on 30 May 2014 in a 1-0 victory against [[Turks and Caicos Islands national football team|Turks and Caicos]] for the [[Caribbean Cup]]. He made his first international goal in the match.
