{{Refimprove|date=August 2016}} {{Infobox venue | stadium_name = TOT Stadium Chaeng Watthana | image = File:TOT Stadium.jpg | location = [[Lak Si District|Lak Si]], [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]] | coordinates = {{coord|13.884179|100.576941|format=dms|type:landmark_scale:3000}} | opened = 2010 | owner = [[TOT Public Company Limited]] | operator = [[TOT Public Company Limited]] | surface = Grass | construction_cost = | former_names = | tenants = | seating_capacity = 5,000<ref>http://stadiumdb.com/stadiums/tha/tot_stadium</ref> | publictransit = {{rint|bangkok|dark red}} [[Lak Si Station|Lak Si]] ''(from 2020)'' }}
'''TOT Stadium Chaeng Watthana''' ({{lang-th|สนามทีโอที สเตเดี้ยม}}) is a football stadium in [[Lak Si District|Lak Si]], [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]]. It is used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches at several competitions and levels and was the home stadium of [[TOT S.C.|TOT Sport Club]], which was disvolved in 2016. The stadium holds 5,000 spectators.<ref>https://pantip.com/topic/33624551</ref><ref>https://sport.mthai.com/tag/%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%82%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5-%E0%B8%AA%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%95%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%A1</ref>
